WITH
	verified_accounts AS (
    	SELECT 
        	accountid
        FROM imhotep.passdailysnapshot 
        WHERE 
        	day = '2024-09-01' -- date_format(date_add('day', -1, CURRENT_DATE), '%Y-%m-%d')
            AND verified = 1
            AND deleted != 1
    ),
    profiles AS (
    	SELECT 
        	acctid AS accountid
            , coalesce(try(resumes[1].locale), '') AS resume_locale
            , CAST(
            	ROW(
                	coalesce(try(regexp_replace(trim(resumes[1].location.city), '\s+', ' ')), '')
            		, coalesce(try(resumes[1].location.admin1), '')
            		, coalesce(try(resumes[1].location.admin2), '')
                    , coalesce(try(resumes[1].location.country), ''))
                AS ROW(
                	city varchar
                    , admin1 varchar
                    , admin2 varchar
                    , country varchar)) AS resume_location
            , coalesce(try(regexp_replace(lower(trim(resumes[1].workexperience[1].title)), '\s+', ' ')), '') AS resume_most_recent_title
            , coalesce(try(regexp_replace(lower(trim(resumes[1].workexperience[1].normalizedtitle)), '\s+', ' ')), '') AS resume_most_recent_normalized_title
 
            , CAST(
            	ROW(
                	coalesce(try(regexp_replace(trim(defaultinfo.contactinformation.location.city), '\s+', ' ')), '')
            		, coalesce(try(defaultinfo.contactinformation.location.admin1), '')
            		, coalesce(try(defaultinfo.contactinformation.location.admin2), '')
                    , coalesce(try(defaultinfo.contactinformation.location.country), ''))
                AS ROW(
                	city varchar
                    , admin1 varchar
                    , admin2 varchar
                    , country varchar)) AS profile_location
 			, coalesce(try(
            	flatten(filter(
                    transform(
                        map_values(normalizeddata['User'].preferences)
                        , p -> coalesce(try(
                        	filter(
                            	transform(
                                	filter(
                                		map_values(p.titles) 
                                		, x -> x.sentiment = 'POSITIVE')
                                    , x -> coalesce(regexp_replace(lower(trim(x.title)), '\s+', ' '), ''))
                                , x -> x != ''))
                            , ARRAY[]))
                    , x -> x IS NOT NULL))[1])
                , '') AS profile_desired_title
            /*
            , coalesce(try(
            	flatten(filter(
                    transform(
                        map_values(normalizeddata['User'].preferences)
                        , p -> coalesce(try(
                        	filter(
                            	transform(
                                	filter(
                                		map_values(p.locations) 
                                		, x -> x.sentiment = 'POSITIVE')
                                    , x -> ARRAY[
                                    	coalesce(try(regexp_replace(trim(x.location.city), '\s+', ' ')), '')
                                        , coalesce(try(x.location.admin1), '')
                                        , coalesce(try(x.location.country), '')])
                                , loc -> any_match(loc, x -> x != '')))
                            , ARRAY[]))
                    , x -> x IS NOT NULL)))
                , ARRAY[]) AS profile_reloc_locations
            */
        FROM jssdi.profile_snapshot
        WHERE 
        	day = '2024-09-01' --date_format(date_add('day', -1, CURRENT_DATE), '%Y-%m-%d')
            AND (
            	-- cardinality(resumes) = 0
            	-- OR (
                	cardinality(resumes) = 1
                    AND resumes[1].resumetype IN ('INDEED_RESUME', 'PARSED')
                    AND resumes[1].state IN ('PUBLIC', 'HIDDEN')
                    AND resumes[1].datecreated > 0
                    AND resumes[1].datemodified > 0
                    AND resumes[1].location.country = 'US'
                    AND resumes[1].locale = 'en_US'
                -- )
             )
    ),
    profile_summary AS (
        SELECT
            p.accountid AS profile_accountid 
            , v.accountid AS verified_accountid
            , IF(profile_desired_title != ''
                , profile_desired_title
                , resume_most_recent_normalized_title) AS best_title
            , CASE
            	WHEN (resume_location.city != '' OR resume_location.admin2 != '')
            			AND resume_location.admin1 != '' 
                		AND resume_location.country = 'US' THEN
                	resume_location
                WHEN (profile_location.city != '' OR profile_location.admin2 != '')
            			AND profile_location.admin1 != '' 
                		AND profile_location.country = 'US' THEN
                	profile_location
                ELSE
                    NULL
            END AS best_location
        FROM 
        	profiles p
            JOIN verified_accounts v ON (p.accountid = v.accountid)
    ),
    clicks AS (
      SELECT acctid as accountid, jobid, sponsored as is_sponsored_click
      FROM datalake.imhotep.clickanalytics
      WHERE unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2023-09-01') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2024-09-01') AND acctid is not null
      LIMIT 1000
	)
    SELECT
    profile_accountid
	, best_title
    , best_location.city
    , best_location.admin1
    , best_location.admin2
    , jobid
    , is_sponsored_click
FROM 
	profile_summary p JOIN clicks c on p.profile_accountid = c.accountid
WHERE 
    
    best_location IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7
ORDER BY 1 DESC limit 10

WITH sub1 as (
    SELECT
    	DATE_FORMAT(FROM_UNIXTIME(ji.unixtime), '%Y-%m-%d') as date,
        tw.tier_0 AS t0,
        tw.tier_1 AS t1,
        tw.tier_2 AS t2,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN
        	ji.status IN ('Closed', 'Done', 'Pending Code Cleanup', 'Pending Closure', 'Pending Analysis', 'Test Paused', 'Test in Progress', 'Pending Prod Release') AND 
            (
              (
                  ji.priority = 'Blocker' AND
                  -- ji.resolutiontimestamp > 0 AND
                  -- last 30 days
                  (ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 <= 30 AND
                  -- SLO days to complete
                  (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) - TRY_CAST(ji.createtimestamp AS BIGINT)) / 86400000 <= 30
              ) OR (
              	  -- Fallback to capture Critical and all other issues until bot updates to prevent data gaps 
                  ji.priority NOT IN ('Blocker') AND
                  -- ji.resolutiontimestamp > 0 AND
                  -- last 30 days
                  (ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 <= 30 AND
                  -- SLO days to complete
                  (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) - TRY_CAST(ji.createtimestamp AS BIGINT)) / 86400000 <= 90
              )
            ) THEN 1 END
        ) AS REM_30,
        COUNT(
        	CASE WHEN
            	ji.status IN ('Closed', 'Done', 'Pending Code Cleanup', 'Pending Closure', 'Pending Analysis', 'Test Paused', 'Test in Progress', 'Pending Prod Release') AND
            	-- ji.resolutiontimestamp > 0 AND
                (ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 <= 30
                THEN 1 END
        ) AS ALL_REM_30,
        COUNT(
        	CASE WHEN
            	(
                    ji.status NOT IN ('Closed', 'Done', 'Pending Code Cleanup', 'Pending Closure', 'Pending Analysis', 'Test Paused', 'Test in Progress', 'Pending Prod Release')
            	    -- OR ji.resolutiontimestamp = 0
                ) AND (
                	(
                    	ji.priority = 'Blocker' AND
                        -- SLO days to complete
                		(ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.createtimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 > 30
                    ) OR (
                    	-- SLO days to complete
                    	ji.priority NOT IN ('Blocker') AND
                		(ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.createtimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 > 90
                    )
                )
                THEN 1 END
        ) AS UNREM
    FROM datalake.imhotep.jiracloudissues AS ji
    JOIN datalake.imhotep.ownershipSnapshot AS ow ON ji.projectkey = ow.key AND ji.day = ow.day
    JOIN datalake.imhotep.teamwrksSnapshot AS tw ON ow.accountablePartyId = tw.teamId AND tw.day = ow.day
    WHERE
        ji.unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('30d') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today') AND
        ow.unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('30d') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today') AND
        tw.unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('30d') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today') AND
        CONTAINS(TRANSFORM(ji.labelstok, s -> LOWER(s)), 'a11y') AND
        NOT CONTAINS(TRANSFORM(ji.labelstok, s -> LOWER(s)), 'a11y-exemption') AND
        -- ((ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 <= 30 OR ji.resolutiontimestamp = 0) AND
        ji.projectkey NOT IN  ('QL', 'A11Y', 'PIED', 'HIGHLANDER', 'JSA11Y', 'EMPA11Y', 'FIM', 'DSYNC', 'CHUBSERV', 'CHUBUI', 'COMMSHUB', 'CHUBSEND') AND
        ji.issuetype = 'Bug' AND
        LOWER(tw.tier_1) NOT IN ('global revenue', 'marketing')
    GROUP BY DATE_FORMAT(FROM_UNIXTIME(ji.unixtime), '%Y-%m-%d'), tw.tier_0, tw.tier_1, tw.tier_2
)

SELECT
	date,
    t0,
    t1,
    t2,
    CASE
    	WHEN ALL_REM_30 IS NULL OR (ALL_REM_30 + UNREM = 0) THEN 100
        ELSE ROUND((CAST(REM_30 AS DECIMAL(10, 2)) / (CAST(ALL_REM_30 AS DECIMAL(10, 2)) + CAST(UNREM AS DECIMAL(10, 2)))) * 100, 2)
    END AS SLO_Score,
    REM_30 AS Within_SLO,
    ALL_REM_30 AS Remediated_Last_30,
    UNREM AS Open_Outside_SLO
FROM sub1
WHERE
	(t0 = 'Indeed') AND
    (''='' OR t1 = '') AND
    (''='' OR t2 = '')
ORDER BY date, t0, t1, t2 ASC

WITH sub1 as (
    SELECT
    	DATE_FORMAT(FROM_UNIXTIME(ji.unixtime), '%Y-%m-%d') as date,
        tw.tier_0 AS t0,
        tw.tier_1 AS t1,
        tw.tier_2 AS t2,
        tw.tier_3 AS t3,
        COUNT(CASE WHEN
        	ji.status IN ('Closed', 'Done', 'Pending Code Cleanup', 'Pending Closure', 'Pending Analysis', 'Test Paused', 'Test in Progress', 'Pending Prod Release') AND 
            (
              (
                  ji.priority = 'Blocker' AND
                  -- ji.resolutiontimestamp > 0 AND
                  -- last 30 days
                  (ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 <= 30 AND
                  -- SLO days to complete
                  (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) - TRY_CAST(ji.createtimestamp AS BIGINT)) / 86400000 <= 30
              ) OR (
              	  -- Fallback to capture Critical and all other issues until bot updates to prevent data gaps 
                  ji.priority NOT IN ('Blocker') AND
                  -- ji.resolutiontimestamp > 0 AND
                  -- last 30 days
                  (ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 <= 30 AND
                  -- SLO days to complete
                  (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) - TRY_CAST(ji.createtimestamp AS BIGINT)) / 86400000 <= 90
              )
            ) THEN 1 END
        ) AS REM_30,
        COUNT(
        	CASE WHEN
            	ji.status IN ('Closed', 'Done', 'Pending Code Cleanup', 'Pending Closure', 'Pending Analysis', 'Test Paused', 'Test in Progress', 'Pending Prod Release') AND
            	-- ji.resolutiontimestamp > 0 AND
                (ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 <= 30
                THEN 1 END
        ) AS ALL_REM_30,
        COUNT(
        	CASE WHEN
            	(
                    ji.status NOT IN ('Closed', 'Done', 'Pending Code Cleanup', 'Pending Closure', 'Pending Analysis', 'Test Paused', 'Test in Progress', 'Pending Prod Release')
            	    -- OR ji.resolutiontimestamp = 0
                ) AND (
                	(
                    	ji.priority = 'Blocker' AND
                        -- SLO days to complete
                		(ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.createtimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 > 30
                    ) OR (
                    	-- SLO days to complete
                    	ji.priority NOT IN ('Blocker') AND
                		(ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.createtimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 > 90
                    )
                )
                THEN 1 END
        ) AS UNREM
    FROM datalake.imhotep.jiracloudissues AS ji
    JOIN datalake.imhotep.ownershipSnapshot AS ow ON ji.projectkey = ow.key AND ji.day = ow.day
    JOIN datalake.imhotep.teamwrksSnapshot AS tw ON ow.accountablePartyId = tw.teamId AND tw.day = ow.day
    WHERE
        ji.unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('30d') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today') AND
        ow.unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('30d') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today') AND
        tw.unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('30d') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today') AND
        CONTAINS(TRANSFORM(ji.labelstok, s -> LOWER(s)), 'a11y') AND
        NOT CONTAINS(TRANSFORM(ji.labelstok, s -> LOWER(s)), 'a11y-exemption') AND
        -- ((ji.unixtime - (TRY_CAST(ji.resolutiontimestamp AS BIGINT) / 1000)) / 86400 <= 30 OR ji.resolutiontimestamp = 0) AND
        ji.projectkey NOT IN  ('QL', 'A11Y', 'PIED', 'HIGHLANDER', 'JSA11Y', 'EMPA11Y', 'FIM', 'DSYNC', 'CHUBSERV', 'CHUBUI', 'COMMSHUB', 'CHUBSEND') AND
        ji.issuetype = 'Bug' AND
        LOWER(tw.tier_1) NOT IN ('global revenue', 'marketing') AND
		tw.tier_3 != 'Unspecified'
    GROUP BY DATE_FORMAT(FROM_UNIXTIME(ji.unixtime), '%Y-%m-%d'), tw.tier_0, tw.tier_1, tw.tier_2, tw.tier_3
)

SELECT
	date,
    t0,
    t1,
    t2,
    t3,
    CASE
    	WHEN ALL_REM_30 IS NULL OR (ALL_REM_30 + UNREM = 0) THEN 100
        ELSE ROUND((CAST(REM_30 AS DECIMAL(10, 2)) / (CAST(ALL_REM_30 AS DECIMAL(10, 2)) + CAST(UNREM AS DECIMAL(10, 2)))) * 100, 2)
    END AS SLO_Score,
    REM_30 AS Within_SLO,
    ALL_REM_30 AS Remediated_Last_30,
    UNREM AS Open_Outside_SLO
FROM sub1
WHERE
	(t0 = 'Indeed') AND
    (''='' OR t1 = '') AND
    (''='' OR t2 = '') AND
    ('Design Systems'='' OR t3 = 'Design Systems')
ORDER BY date, t0, t1, t2, t3 ASC

WITH 

calendar AS (

    SELECT
    	DATE_ADD('day', days, DATE('2023-10-01')) AS snapshot_date, 1 AS tmpJoin
    FROM
        (SELECT SEQUENCE(0, 1500) AS d)
    CROSS JOIN 
    	UNNEST (d) as t(days)
    WHERE
    	DATE_ADD('day', days, DATE('2023-10-01')) <= CURRENT_DATE

),

engagement_daily AS (

    SELECT	
        DATE(activity_time) AS activity_date,
        advertiser_id,
        subscription_tier,
        usage_category,
        subscription_id,
        SUM(contact_sent) AS contacts_sent,
        SUM(positive_response) AS positive_responses
    FROM 
        datalake.employer_analytics_platform.xpa_fct_sourcing_engagement xpa
    WHERE 
        activity_time >= DATE('2023-11-01')
        AND subscription_tier IN ('Standard','Professional')
        AND is_free_contact = 0
    GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4, 5

)

SELECT 
	CAST(snapshot_date AS varchar) AS snapshot_date,
    subscription_tier,
    usage_category,
    SUM(contacts_sent) AS contacts_sent,
    SUM(positive_responses) AS pos_resp,
    COUNT(DISTINCT advertiser_id) AS num_adv,
    TRY((SUM(contacts_sent) * 1.0000) / COUNT(DISTINCT advertiser_id)) AS contacts_per_adv,
    TRY((SUM(contacts_sent) * 1.0000) / COUNT(DISTINCT subscription_id)) AS contacts_per_sub,
    TRY((SUM(positive_responses) * 1.0000) / SUM(contacts_sent)) AS pos_resp_rate
FROM 
	calendar
INNER JOIN
	engagement_daily
        	ON engagement_daily.activity_date > DATE_ADD('day', -14, calendar.snapshot_date)
            AND engagement_daily.activity_date <= calendar.snapshot_date
WHERE 
	snapshot_date >= DATE('2024-01-01')
GROUP BY 1, 2, 3
ORDER BY 1, 2, 3

WITH 
  q1 AS(
      SELECT DISTINCT DATE(trial_start_date) AS date
      FROM datalake.analysis.dim_resume_trial_attribution
      WHERE trial_start_date BETWEEN DATE('2023-01-01') AND FROM_UNIXTIME(IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today'))
  ),
  q2 AS(
      SELECT DISTINCT
          DATE(trial_start_date) AS date,
          trial_subscription_id,
          attributed_subscription_id,
          attribution_date,
          DATE_DIFF('day', trial_start_date, attribution_date) AS days_to_convert
      FROM datalake.analysis.dim_resume_trial_attribution
      WHERE trial_start_date BETWEEN DATE('2023-01-01') AND FROM_UNIXTIME(IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today'))
  )
SELECT 
	q1.date,
    COUNT(DISTINCT IF(q2.days_to_convert <= 180, q2.attributed_subscription_id, NULL)) / CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT q2.trial_subscription_id) AS double) AS trial_conversion_rate_180d,
    COUNT(DISTINCT IF(q2.days_to_convert <= 30, q2.attributed_subscription_id, NULL)) / CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT q2.trial_subscription_id) AS double) AS trial_conversion_rate_30d
FROM
	q1, 
    q2
WHERE 
	q2.date BETWEEN q1.date - INTERVAL '42' DAY AND q1.date - INTERVAL '14' DAY
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 1

	and dcr.numhiresMade> '0'
    and closedJobReason = 'notIndeed'
group by 1
)
,job_id_job_hash_mapping as (
SELECT 
	jobhash_underscore, max(agg_job_id) as agg_job_id
FROM datalake.imhotep.job_id_job_hash_mapping
WHERE unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2024-10-23') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2024-10-24')
	and jobhash_underscore in (select distinct job_hash from cjs)
group by 1 
)
,jam as (
select 
	agg_job_id,
    max(job_product) as job_product,
    max(job_country_code) as job_country_code,
    sum(clicks) as clicks,
    sum(apply_starts) as apply_starts,

where day between '2022-04-01' and 'today'	
	and agg_job_id in (select distinct agg_job_id from job_id_job_hash_mapping)
group by 1 
)

,view as (
select 
	job_id_job_hash_mapping.agg_job_id,
    coalesce(applies,0) as applies,
    coalesce(apply_starts,0) as apply_starts,
    coalesce(clicks,0) as clicks,
    numhiresMade,
    numHiresMadeIndeed,
    numHiresMadeExternal,
    job_product,
    job_country_code,
    max_job_age_days
from cjs 
join job_id_job_hash_mapping on job_id_job_hash_mapping.jobhash_underscore = cjs.job_hash
left join jam
	on job_id_job_hash_mapping.agg_job_id = jam.agg_job_id
)

with js as (
select 
    account_id
    , sourcing_eligible 
    , has_first_and_last_name_flag
    , location_geocoded_flag 
    , has_occ_category_suid
    , has_skills_suid
    , has_credential_suid
    , has_min_pay
    , wordcount_over_50
from (
    select 
          this_month.account_id 
          , minimally_complete
          , if(sourcing_eligible, 1, 0) sourcing_eligible
          
          --First and last name are filled out
          , case when (has_resume_first_name and has_resume_last_name) then 1 else 0 end as has_first_and_last_name_flag
          
          -- Location is geocoded to city, postal, or address precision
          --   , case when resume_location_geocode_precision like 'POSTAL' or resume_location_geocode_precision like 'ADDRESS' then 1 else 0 end as location_geocoded_flag
          , case when if(resume_location_geocode_precision in ('POSTAL', 'ADDRESS'), 1, 0)
                    + if(profile_location_geocode_precision in ('POSTAL', 'ADDRESS'), 1, 0) 
                    > 0 then 1 else 0 end as location_geocoded_flag
          
          --User-submitted OR resume-extracted occupation category SUID
          , case when coalesce(CARDINALITY(normalizeddata_resumeextracted_occupations_suids_array),0) 
                    + coalesce(CARDINALITY(normalizeddata_user_pos_occupations_suids_array),0)
                    + coalesce(CARDINALITY(normalizeddata_user_preferences_occupations_suids_array),0) 
                    > 0 then 1 else 0 end as has_occ_category_suid
          
          --User-submitted OR resume-extracted skills SUID
          , case when coalesce(CARDINALITY(normalizeddata_resumeextracted_skills_suids_array),0) 
                    + coalesce(CARDINALITY(normalizeddata_user_pos_skills_suids_array),0) 
                    + coalesce(CARDINALITY(filter(resume_skills_array_taxonomy_concept_title_suid, q -> q!='')),0) 
                    > 0 then 1 else 0 end as has_skills_suid
          
          --User-submitted OR resume-extracted credential SUID (education OR certification OR license)
          , case when coalesce(CARDINALITY(filter(normalizeddata_resumeextracted_certifications_suids_array, q -> q!='')),0)
                    + coalesce(CARDINALITY(normalizeddata_user_pos_certifications_suids_array),0)
                    + coalesce(CARDINALITY(normalizeddata_resumeextracted_licenses_suids_array),0) 
                    + coalesce(CARDINALITY(normalizeddata_user_pos_licenses_suids_array),0)
                    + coalesce(CARDINALITY(filter(resume_education_0_degrees_taxonomy_concept_degree_suid, q -> q!='')),0)
                    + coalesce(CARDINALITY(filter(normalizeddata_user_pos_educations_degree_suids_array, q -> q!='')),0)
                    + coalesce(CARDINALITY(resume_military_array_branch),0)
                    > 0 then 1 else 0 end as has_credential_suid
          
          --User-submmited desired minimum pay
          , case when coalesce(CARDINALITY(normalizeddata_user_desiredminpay_array),0) > 0 then 1 else 0 end as has_min_pay
          
          --Resume wordcount over 50
          , case when resume_total_wordcount > 50 then 1 else 0 end as wordcount_over_50
          
    from datalake.imhotep.js_fact_store_snapshot_prod this_month
    where 
        hour between '2024-06-30' and '2024-07-01'
        --and not minimally_complete
          -- and upper(resume_geo_country) = 'US'
    )
group by 1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9
),

uswr as (
    select 
        distinct account_id 
    from datalake.imhotep.usersession_with_reach
    where hour between '2024-06-01' and '2024-07-01'
        and (not (contains(grp, 'spider') or contains(grp, 'privileged')) or grp is null)
        and coalesce(islikelybot,0) != 1
        and account_id > 0
)

select 
    sourcing_eligible + has_first_and_last_name_flag + location_geocoded_flag + has_occ_category_suid + has_skills_suid + has_credential_suid + has_min_pay + wordcount_over_50 as num_attr 
    , if(uswr.account_id is not null, 1, 0) active_flag 
    , count(distinct js.account_id) as num_js 
from js 
left join uswr 
    on js.account_id = uswr.account_id 
group by 1,2

sum(a.impressions) sj_impressions,

where a.activity_month between cast('2023-10-01' as date) and cast('2024-09-30' as date)
and a.advertiser_id in (72681337)
group by 1,2,3,4
),

oj_id as (select distinct
a.job_id
from datalake.core.jobs_dim_job_attributes_latest a
where source_id in (1008003) and upper(a.job_country) IN ('IT') --and source_id in (2071173,17291098,19548234,10719845)

with rules as (SELECT distinct rule_id
FROM datalake.imhotep.waldorulesnapshot
WHERE unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2024-10-01') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2024-10-08') 
AND CONTAINS(rule_tags, 'cat_risk') AND type=0 AND visibility='nowhere'),

matches as (SELECT distinct jobid, ruleid
FROM datalake.imhotep.waldorulematch
WHERE unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2024-10-01') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2024-10-08')),

sj as (SELECT distinct jobid, 1 as nowhere
FROM datalake.imhotep.searchablejobs
WHERE unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2024-10-01') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2024-10-08')
AND waldovisibilitylevel='nowhere' AND feedid!=50461),

fiji as (select distinct jobid, feedSourceId, feedid, sourceid
from datalake.imhotep.fijievents 
where unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2024-10-01') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2024-10-08')
AND event='jobScanned'),

fraudulent_jobs as (select matches.jobid, 1 as fraud
from matches
inner join rules
ON matches.ruleid=rules.rule_id
inner join sj
ON matches.jobid = sj.jobid
where sj.nowhere=1)

select feedSourceId, CAST(sourceid as VARCHAR) as sourceid, CAST(feedid as VARCHAR) as feedid, count() as numJobs, sum(fraud) as numFrauds, sum(fraud) * 100.000/count() as fraud_percent
from (select fiji.*, coalesce(fraud, 0) as fraud
      from fiji
      left join fraudulent_jobs
      on fiji.jobid=fraudulent_jobs.jobid)
group by feedSourceId, sourceid, feedid
ORDER BY fraud_percent DESC

WITH 
most_recent_appid AS (
	SELECT j.appid, MAX(j.unixtime) AS lastStartupUnixtime 
    FROM datalake.imhotep.javaruntimeversions j
    WHERE 
    	j.unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2023-01-01') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today') 
        AND j.env='prod'
	GROUP BY appid
),
most_recent_appname AS (
	SELECT j.appinstance, MAX(j.unixtime) AS lastStartupUnixtime 
    FROM datalake.imhotep.javaruntimeversions j
    WHERE 
    	j.unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2023-01-01') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today') 
        AND j.env='prod'
	GROUP BY appinstance
),
java_starts_appid AS (
    SELECT 
        FROM_UNIXTIME(j.unixtime) AS startupTime,
        j.appid,
        j.gitRepo AS gitRepository,
        CASE	
            WHEN javaversion LIKE '1.8.%' THEN 8
            WHEN javaversion LIKE '11.%' THEN 11
            WHEN javaversion LIKE '17.%' THEN 17 
            ELSE -1
        END AS javaMajorVersion
    FROM datalake.imhotep.javaruntimeversions j 
    JOIN 
        most_recent_appid m ON j.appid=m.appid AND m.lastStartupUnixtime=j.unixtime
    WHERE 
        j.unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2023-01-01') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today')
        AND j.env='prod'
    ORDER BY startupTime DESC
),
java_starts_appname AS (
    SELECT 
        FROM_UNIXTIME(j.unixtime) AS startupTime,
        j.appinstance,
        j.gitRepo AS gitRepository,
        CASE	
            WHEN javaversion LIKE '1.8.%' THEN 8
            WHEN javaversion LIKE '11.%' THEN 11
            WHEN javaversion LIKE '17.%' THEN 17 
            ELSE -1
        END AS javaMajorVersion
    FROM datalake.imhotep.javaruntimeversions j 
    JOIN 
        most_recent_appname m ON j.appinstance=m.appinstance AND m.lastStartupUnixtime=j.unixtime
    WHERE 
        j.unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2023-01-01') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today')
        AND j.env='prod'
    ORDER BY startupTime DESC
)

SELECT 
    j.startupTime,
	srs.applicationId,
    srs.applicationName,
    j.javaMajorVersion,
    srs.giturl as gitRepository,
    srs.runtimeType,
    srs.criticalityTier,
    srs.applicationType,
    (srs.applicationType = 'CRONJOB' and CARDINALITY(srs.orcdeploymentnameprod) > 0) isCronJobInProd,
    srs.lifeCycle,
    srs.state,
    srs.teamId,
    t.displayname, 
    t.intakejira AS teamJira, t.email AS teamEmail, t.usersslackchannel AS teamSlack,
    t.tier_0, t.tier_1, t.tier_2, t.tier_3, t.tier_4, 
    t.engineeringleadldap AS ldapTDM, 
    t.productleadldap AS ldapPM, 
    t.programleadldap AS ldapPGM, 
    t.technologyleadldap AS ldapTLA
FROM datalake.imhotep.serviceregistrysnapshots srs
LEFT JOIN datalake.imhotep.teamwrkssnapshot t ON srs.teamId=t.teamId

LEFT JOIN java_starts_appid j ON srs.applicationId=j.appid
WHERE

WITH tickets AS (
    SELECT 
    	originalissuekey AS jiraId,
        LTRIM(REGEXP_EXTRACT(labels, '(appid--([0-9a-fA-F]{8}\b-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}\b-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}\b-[0-9a-fA-F]{4}\b-[0-9a-fA-F]{12}))'), 'appid--') AS applicationId
    FROM imhotep.jiraactions
    WHERE 
        action='create' 
        AND reporterusername='mredding' 
        AND labels LIKE '%Java17_Migration%' 
        AND unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2023-11-01') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today')
), processed AS (
    SELECT 
        FROM_UNIXTIME(ja.unixtime) AS action_time, 
        ja.originalissuekey AS originalTicketId, 
        ja.issuekey AS currentTicketId, 
        ja.action, 
        ja.prevstatus, 
        ja.status, 
        ja.resolution
    FROM imhotep.jiraactions ja
    WHERE
        ja.originalissuekey IN (SELECT jiraId FROM tickets)
        AND ((ja.action='create') OR (ja.action='update' AND prevstatus!=status))
        AND unixtime BETWEEN IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('2023-11-01') AND IMHOTEP_UNIXTIME('today')
), most_recent AS (
	SELECT originalTicketId, MAX(action_time) AS action_time FROM processed
    GROUP BY originalTicketId
)

SELECT p.*, t.applicationId
FROM processed p
JOIN 
    most_recent m ON p.originalTicketId=m.originalTicketId AND p.action_time=m.action_time
JOIN
	tickets t ON p.originalTicketId=t.jiraId
